Author: nhungtruong379
Title: [ANN - ICO] INCREMINT: Solves the ICO credibility problem. Goodbye ICO Scams.
Body: Incremint is the ICO for smart investors.  The Problem: ICOs are unregulated, and backers have limited options to mitigate their risks.  INCREMINT's Solution: Blockchain Escrow.  INCREMINT believes ICOs will continue to thrive and that the accountability problem can be solved!

Author: PeterKh
Title: [ANN - ICO] INCREMINT: Solves the ICO credibility problem. Goodbye ICO Scams.
Body: One of the critical issues that we've been hearing from the crypto community regarding our project: "Why is Incremint not using its own escrow platform for Mint token sale?" Our response has been that we could not use Incremint platform because it had not been deployed yet.  However, we acknowledge the importance of being the adopters of own “medicine”.  As a result, we have decided to extend the date of our main token sale such that we can use the Incremint escrow platform for the funds that we collect from Mint token buyers.  Thanks! Peter COO, Incremint

Author: nhungtruong379
Title: [ANN - ICO] INCREMINT: Solves the ICO credibility problem. Goodbye ICO Scams.
Body: Many believe that the bans on advertising, most recently initiated on Facebook, and soon to be on Google are a result of a lack of accountability in the ICO space and the high percentage of people are have invested in faulty ICOs.  Incremint's decentralized escrow platform solves both of these problems.

Author: PeterKh
Title: [ANN - ICO] INCREMINT: Solves the ICO credibility problem. Goodbye ICO Scams.
Body: Hi everyone!  Thanks for the questions about DAICO. Our project is indeed conceptually in line with Vitalik's proposal. We were very excited when we saw his "Explanation of DAICOs" as we've been working on this project since last summer.  Our platform will be offering more options/flexibility compared to the basic solution suggested by DAICO proposal. You can see on our website (incremint.io) and on the second image above the item comparison of our platform to DAICO.  The key distinguishing features include the ability to store funds in fiat escrow, pre-agreed milestones, releases in tranches, flexibility on voting parameters and ability to address force majeure situations.  Also, we will be a ready to use audited solution.  Happy to answer any other questions.  Thanks! Peter Incremint, COO

Author: PeterKh
Title: [ANN - ICO] INCREMINT: Solves the ICO credibility problem. Goodbye ICO Scams.
Body: We're building a network of fiat escrow agents to allow for a fiat capability. The agents will be contractually bound to respect the results of token holder voting.
